<br>
this thread is a great example of that.<br>
<br>
people think that changes made to skalds recently had some real impact.  the fact is that there was two changes only that made real impacts, and that was the lessening of the power cost and the timer of our DDs.  the 50 songs spec doing a lot more damage, as was claimed, isn't true.  the extra 60 life doesn't matter.  all that matters is the 15 second timers and lower costs so we aren't oop every single fight.  skalds are not overpowerd.  we're not even close to a minstrel.  and due to the changes we will never be.  if they had given us the faster DDs from last changes, AND shield spec, AND 2.0 points instead of 1.5, AND an overpowered RA like sos, AND an instant stun in addition to our instant mez, then we would be almost as overpowered like minstrels.  but not quite.  but some people just dont get that, as they really dont know what minstrels can or should do despite having a rank 6 minstrel.<br>
<br>
there are people here still harping about switching mastery of block for dodger.  the truth is that this does nothing substantial for skalds except make us better duelers.  and then only if you're rank 9 or above, as you need to buy purge, IP, AP3, (7,2) MoPain 2, (8,0) tough2, avoid magic 2 (8,<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> before you buy dodger.  we're already the best duelers in midgard.  and we can beat most other classes in the other realms with the notable exception of high rank minstrels.  what good does it do to make rank 9 skalds better duelers?  no good.  you're not rank 9 and neither am i.<br>
<br>
which brings us to minstrels.  the claim was made in this thread that skalds are superior in some way to minstrels, backed up with the claim that the person had a high rank skald and minstrel.  the fact is that this person doesn't know what's going on despite his ranks.  skalds have worse group support abilities, by a huge factor, than a minstrel, and at high rank skalds can't beat a minstrel one on one either.  my skald obliterates minstrels, just as all skalds do, if they're rank 4 or below.  it's a joke.  but at rank 7 it's not a joke.  and the rank 10 minstrel on my server tears me apart.  that mastery of block that everyone thinks is such ass?  well if you have mob3 like that minstrel does you block, and you block quite a bit.  it can be accurately stated that a skald is a superior assist train member, but if a minstrel was part of an assist train they would be playing poorly anyway so that is an invalid argument.  much like a skald is being played poorly if they are part of an assist train, but that is getting off track.<br>
<br>
there are a lot of people with a lot of ideas in this forum, and in all forums.  the problem is that not all of those ideas are equally vaild.  everyone is not equal, and that is not fair, but that's just how it is.<br>
<br>
hopefully the &quot;style review&quot;, whatever that is and whenever that happens, will give us a new LW type spec in midgard.  maybe even for all original mid melees.  the one i posted in the styles review would be good starting point.  i would probably even bother to play my skald for more than just farming sariloc if they would make a legitimate change like that. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.paradoxguild.com/images/phlsig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=767.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=767.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=767.topic&start=61&stop=78>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=767.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=767.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=767.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=767.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.threadControl?topicID=767.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><